<li>Thinking of you and your family during this heartbreaking time. May God wrap you in His loving arms.</li>
<li>He was a wonderful man, and his memory will be a blessing.  Praying for comfort and healing for you all.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, may God's grace comfort you and your family.</li>
<li>Sending you love and prayers during this difficult time. May God's peace be with you.</li>
<li>May God’s love surround you and your family, providing comfort and strength during your grief.</li>
<li>I offer my sincere condolences.  May your cherished memories bring you solace.</li>
<li>Please accept my deepest sympathy.  May God's grace give you strength.</li>
<li>May the love and support of family and friends sustain you. God bless you.</li>
<li> Sending prayers for comfort and peace to you and your family.</li>
<li> My heart aches for your loss.  May God's love surround you.</li>
<li> May God give you strength during this difficult time. We are here for you.</li>
